						Oceanic Investment Management LTD Lowered By $1.76 Million Its Devon Energy New (DVN) Position, Last Week STMicroelectronics NV (ADR) (STM) Coverage - Bibey Post								

























 























































Trending Stock News
Penny Stock News
Market News
Stock News






Oceanic Investment Management LTD Lowered By $1.76 Million Its Devon Energy New (DVN) Position, Last Week STMicroelectronics NV (ADR) (STM) Coverage


					
						July 26, 2017 - By test

Oceanic Investment Management Ltd decreased Devon Energy Corp New (DVN) stake by 16.93% reported in 2016Q4 SEC filing. Oceanic Investment Management Ltd sold 39,000 shares as Devon Energy Corp New (DVN)’s stock declined 13.09%. The Oceanic Investment Management Ltd holds 191,400 shares with $8.74 million value, down from 230,400 last quarter. Devon Energy Corp New now has $18.02B valuation. The stock increased 0.03% or $0.01 during the last trading session, reaching $32.99. About 6.26 million shares traded or 7.19% up from the average. Devon Energy Corp (NYSE:DVN) has risen 13.24% since July 26, 2016 and is uptrending. It has underperformed by 3.46% the S&P500.







Among 11 analysts covering STMicroelectronics (NYSE:STM), 6 have Buy rating, 2 Sell and 3 Hold. Therefore 55% are positive. STMicroelectronics had 18 analyst reports since July 22, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. The stock of STMicroelectronics NV (ADR) (NYSE:STM) has “Hold” rating given on Wednesday, August 5 by Zacks. Craig Hallum maintained it with “Buy” rating and $11 target in Thursday, October 27 report. The stock has “Buy” rating by Craig Hallum on Friday, April 28. Robert W. Baird upgraded the stock to “Outperform” rating in Monday, October 10 report. The stock of STMicroelectronics NV (ADR) (NYSE:STM) earned “Buy” rating by Natixis on Monday, September 14. The rating was upgraded by Stifel Nicolaus to “Buy” on Tuesday, June 27. On Friday, October 14 the stock rating was maintained by Craig Hallum with “Buy”. The stock has “Buy” rating by J.P. Morgan on Tuesday, July 11. The stock of STMicroelectronics NV (ADR) (NYSE:STM) earned “Overweight” rating by JP Morgan on Tuesday, July 11. The firm has “Hold” rating given on Friday, October 30 by Craig Hallum. See STMicroelectronics NV (ADR) (NYSE:STM) latest ratings:
